title: Ambisonic After Dark
description: 20 HD Ambient Sound Effects with a large selection of evening Crickets, Cicadas, from urban and residential areas.
longDescription:
• From 24/96 Sound Effects. Ambisonic Surround After Dark features 20 HD Ambient Sound Effects with a large selection of evening Crickets and Cicadas, from urban and residential areas. PREVIEW


  • Recorded with a Brahma Ambisonic Microphone and a Zoom F8 recorder and downloads in 2 configurations: (20) .WAV Ambisonic B format (AmbiX FOA SN3D with ACN ordering 44.1 kHz, 16bit ), and (20) .WAV Stereo (L-R) All tracks are 1 minute long and are edited to loop seamlessly. All new and original recordings. Drag and drop to add 3D immersive sound to any project. Need custom Ambisonic tracks for your project? Drop us a line! http://2496sfx.com
technicalDetails:
Features: 20 AmbiX files ( FOA SN3D with ACN ordering 44.1 kHz, 16bit) + 20 Stereo versions

Number of Audio Waves: 40

Number of Audio Cues: 40

Sample Rate/Bit Rate: 44.1 kHz, 16bit AmbiX and Stereo WAVs

Do Sound FX Loop: No

Minutes of Audio Provided: 40

Supported Development Platforms: Audio files are compatible with any platform

Supported Target Build Platforms: Audio files are compatible with any target build platforms
